{"Id":836402,"Title":"霓裳中序第一·城东人家艺菊得异种，花径尺有咫，重跗叠鄂，赪若明霞，余瓣四垂，蹁跹尽态，名曰羽衣舞。龙伯欲以此调写之，未数日遽即世。霜腴既槁，露迹同晞，乃为补题，并寄哀愫","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"金兆蕃","Context":"神山正怨极。幻落秋篱簪未得。红艳亭亭似昔。又倦亸舞鬟，娇留仙褶。轻鸿浅立。证断钗寒圃重谪。惊秾丽，拂珊倚玉，奈此好颜色。萧瑟。暮年词笔。试想像、琼葩径尺。西风催送过翼。笛碎愁心，酒酹吟魄。耐霜霜更急。展锦字残红泪湿。琼楼夜，霓裳重按，念我酒垆侧。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"霓裳中序第一","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"d02a63f2ab5423040c8c51ff6f8eb0f3","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":4907531,"Sentence":"琼楼夜，霓裳重按，念我酒垆侧。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qióng lóu yè ，nǐ cháng chóng àn ，niàn wǒ jiu lú cè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":14,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907517,"Sentence":"神山正怨极。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shén shān zhēng yuàn jǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907519,"Sentence":"红艳亭亭似昔。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gōng yàn tǐng tǐng shì xī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907521,"Sentence":"轻鸿浅立。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qīng hóng jiān lì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907524,"Sentence":"萧瑟。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiāo sè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907525,"Sentence":"暮年词笔。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mù nián cǐ bi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907527,"Sentence":"西风催送过翼。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xī fēng cuī sòng guō yì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":10,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907529,"Sentence":"耐霜霜更急。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"nài shuāng shuāng gēng jǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":12,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907518,"Sentence":"幻落秋篱簪未得。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huàn là qīu lǐ zān wèi dé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4907520,"Sentence":"又倦亸舞鬟，娇留仙褶。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":n